title: GE Griffin A Conspiratorial View of History Austin off-mic sound
description:
This is the same talk as in previous torrents which either no one can or no one wants to seed. Official title: "A Conspiratorial View of History, As Explained by the Conspirators Themselves"

The video would benefit from the addition of hard-coded English subtitles, because of the off-microphone sound quality. (An effort has been made here to enhance the original soundtrack.)

The presentation has been made at other times also, with better sound pickup. But the audience enthusiasm in Austin and interaction with Griffin are great.

Xvid 640x480
AC3 96 kbps
1h 58m 34s without lengthy introductions and with complete questions session
